item.title: How do i make my server work with silabs stuff?
item.dc:creator: @barrage_time barrage time
item.description:
@barrage_time wrote:

silabs stuff = New RuneScape items im assuming.

Did you used to have the new RuneScape items on your server if so go back to using Silabsoft client v.4 .

If not then you need to add all the items that you want to item.cfg and then they should work.

You could just download someone elses client and use there items but you will have to do the same thing anway.

Good luck on this.

[quote=“xXx gl0wi xXx, post:2, topic:172324”]get a source with silab ^^
